creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Discover a vibrant community for parents and pregnant women.

A wealth of information about parenting, pregnancy, and baby development is now at your fingertips. With a single touch, find credible advice from our experienced community, and rich articles from experts. A pregnancy and baby trackers intelligently follows your child's amazing journey and provides support every step of the way.

Empower a happy and healthy pregnancy with our pregnancy tracker. From baby names to health and food guides, our supportive community is a wish-come-true for parents-to-be.

Find a treasure trove of information for parents: nutrition advice, activities, and in-depth guides that cover your every concern. Articles on theAsianparent deliver expert advice on your most urgent questions from pregnancy to child development.

theAsianparent believes that everyone deserves a positive journey from pregnancy to birth to every year of parenting. Moms and dads should have access to the latest science, and the collective wisdom of millions of parents who share the experience of parenthood.


theAsianparent features:

👶PREGNANCY TRACKER AND BABY TRACKER 🤰
- Ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy journey with our pregnancy tracker.
- Never miss what to expect every day with our pregnancy calendar. Watch out for baby's first kick!
- Track your baby's growth day-by-day until age 7 with our baby tracker.
- Keep tabs on baby's development from pregnancy until your child is 7 years old.

👪INTERACT WITH OTHER PARENTS 💏
- Make life easier with parenting tips.
- Get advice on baby care, breastfeeding, and more.
- Be a part of our parenting community together with child health professionals and experienced parents.
- Share your own experiences to guide and help your fellow parents.

📖 FAMILY AND PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Read parenting articles full of useful tips, written with up-to-date research on popular topics.
- Get access to expertly crafted guides on parenting, nutrition and more.
- The most amazing feed of articles will keep you engaged for hours.
- Find baby guides and articles about each month of your baby's development. Stay informed about your baby's milestones and nutritional needs, as well as red flags.

🥘FOOD AND NUTRITION🥛
- Stay on top of nutritional needs for pregnant women and babies.
- Learn about what food is safe to eat during pregnancy, confinement and when you're breastfeeding.
- Make sure nutritional needs are met for pregnant women and children under five.

🎉 GREAT GIFTS! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding. That's why we have attractive prizes for you to win on our app!
- Participate in contests and giveaways, and you could win awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a safe and private parent network, away from the eyes of your frenemies!
- Enjoy photo stickers that you can click and share!
- Sing along to cute videos and songs!
- Avoid the dangers of other video streaming services and enjoy a wealth of videos made for children here.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest community of Asian parents in the world.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Dear parents, we have 3 exciting updates for you:

1.Give our freshly-baked “Recipe feature” a try. Suggestions and tags will tell you if the dish is made for children or safe for mums-to-be.

2.Wish you could peek inside mummy’s tummy to see your baby? Now you can! Our exciting 3D feature will give you a surreal experience of how your little one is growing in your bump!

3.Too tired to type? With our new voice-to-text feature, you can now search the content of our app with your voice!

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Discover a vibrant community for parents and pregnant women.

A wealth of information about parenting, pregnancy, and baby development is now at your fingertips. With a single touch, find credible advice from our experienced community, and rich articles from experts. A pregnancy and baby trackers intelligently follows your child's amazing journey and provides support every step of the way.

Empower a happy and healthy pregnancy with our pregnancy tracker. From baby names to health and food guides, our supportive community is a wish-come-true for parents-to-be.

Find a treasure trove of information for parents: nutrition advice, activities, and in-depth guides that cover your every concern. Articles on theAsianparent deliver expert advice on your most urgent questions from pregnancy to child development.

theAsianparent believes that everyone deserves a positive journey from pregnancy to birth to every year of parenting. Moms and dads should have access to the latest science, and the collective wisdom of millions of parents who share the experience of parenthood.


theAsianparent features:

👶PREGNANCY TRACKER AND BABY TRACKER 🤰
- Ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy journey with our pregnancy tracker.
- Never miss what to expect every day with our pregnancy calendar. Watch out for baby's first kick!
- Track your baby's growth day-by-day until age 7 with our baby tracker.
- Keep tabs on baby's development from pregnancy until your child is 7 years old.

👪INTERACT WITH OTHER PARENTS 💏
- Make life easier with parenting tips.
- Get advice on baby care, breastfeeding, and more.
- Be a part of our parenting community together with child health professionals and experienced parents.
- Share your own experiences to guide and help your fellow parents.

📖 FAMILY AND PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Read parenting articles full of useful tips, written with up-to-date research on popular topics.
- Get access to expertly crafted guides on parenting, nutrition and more.
- The most amazing feed of articles will keep you engaged for hours.
- Find baby guides and articles about each month of your baby's development. Stay informed about your baby's milestones and nutritional needs, as well as red flags.

🥘FOOD AND NUTRITION🥛
- Stay on top of nutritional needs for pregnant women and babies.
- Learn about what food is safe to eat during pregnancy, confinement and when you're breastfeeding.
- Make sure nutritional needs are met for pregnant women and children under five.

🎉 GREAT GIFTS! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding. That's why we have attractive prizes for you to win on our app!
- Participate in contests and giveaways, and you could win awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a safe and private parent network, away from the eyes of your frenemies!
- Enjoy photo stickers that you can click and share!
- Sing along to cute videos and songs!
- Avoid the dangers of other video streaming services and enjoy a wealth of videos made for children here.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest community of Asian parents in the world.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Enjoy your pregnancy and parenting journey with our Asian parents community.

All parents, especially pregnant women, can use theAsianparent to find credible information from our experienced parenting community. Many questions, from nutrition to fetal development to growth, can be difficult to answer for new parents. theAsianparent’s pregnancy and baby development app can help you along the way.

Our pregnancy tracker helps you ensure a happy and healthy pregnancy while the parent community helps you through every step. From the meaning of baby’s name to health to food guides, our community supports parents and parents-to-be.

Find what activities, food, and medicines are safe for pregnant women, and everything you need for your growing baby. Guides and articles on theAsianparent provide expert, curated advices on everything from pregnancy to food choices.

theAsianparent community believes in a healthy pregnancy to parenting experience, that every parent should have access to scientifically accurate information, and in the collective wisdom of millions of parents.

theAsianparent features:

👪SUPPORTIVE PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Ask your concerns about pregnancy & baby care, breastfeeding, ovulation, baby’s feeding schedule and more. Get the answers for other experienced parents within minutes!
- Share your parenting journey to the community. Guide and help a fellow parent based on your own experiences.

👶TRACKING PREGNANCY & BABY DEVELOPMENT 🤰
- Pregnancy tracker to ensure a healthy, happy pregnancy.
- Pregnancy calendar so you’ll know what to expect day by day until due date - the aches and pains as well as the joys like experiencing baby’s first kick!
- Baby tracker to track his/her growth and milestones day-by-day until age 7.

🥘FIND OUT SAFE FOOD & DELICIOUS RECIPES🥛
- Safe food for pregnant women, nursing mothers, postpartum, or for babies and children.
- Make sure nutrition needs are being met from foods that are safe for pregnant women and children under 5.
- Find out delicious recipes that are suitable for pregnancy, postpartum, and breastfeeding. You start weaning your baby? We have many weaning food recipes ready for you!

🤰SUPPORTING HEALTHY PREGNANCY👣
- Keep a track of your baby's movements and record it with our new baby kick counter.
- Having 3 sessions of kick counting a day is advised to know your baby's activeness & health.
- Had a miscarriage or stillbirth? We got your back, Mothers, supporting you with our healing mode.

📖 FAMILY & PARENTING ARTICLES 📱
- Parenting articles full of useful tips, based on the most advanced parenting research, to make life easier.
- Nutrition guides, expertly crafted scientific parenting advice and what’s happening around you - we cover it all.
- All motherhood needs in the most amazing feed of articles that will keep you engaged for hours.
- Baby guides and articles for each month of your baby’s development, so you can stay informed about milestones, diet, activities, vaccinations, as well as red flags.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Share photos in a parent network, away from the nagging eyes of your frenemies!
- Add stickers & frames to your photos and share to your loved ones!
- Enjoy informative videos and popular songs that you can play in background with your little one!
- More kid-safe videos here help parents avoid the danger of other video streaming services.

🎉JOIN CONTESTS & WIN GREAT PRIZES! 🙌
- Parenting should be rewarding, that’s why you can win really cool gifts on our app.
- Contests and giveaways with practical and awesome gifts like strollers, staycations, and much more!
- Join many exciting games held within the community. Grab the prizes & enjoy your parenting journey in more fun way.

Download theAsianparent app today and be a part of the largest parenting community of Asian Parents in the world.

We are super excited about our new releases and can’t wait for you to try them.
1. Introducing VIP Parents:
Here are the key benefits of becoming a VIP member:
- VIP Credits
- Tiktok Integration for VIP Users
- VIP Panel Polls
2. Presenting pregnancy tracker in a brand new look.

You must be having questions about baby feeding schedule, baby poo, pee, etc. Fret not; we are here to help you with everything.

Sleep Tracker: Use our baby sleep tracker that helps you track and learn about your baby’s sleep habits, and provides tips on improving them.
Diaper tracker: Identify baby’s poop & pee patterns, but it can also help you plan the diaper expenses accordingly.
Baby Feeding Tracker: It helps you track your baby’s feeding schedule in one place, monitor the time you spend nursing, how often your baby is feeding, which breast he/she last fed on, and much more.

So, start logging your baby's growth today on our new trackers to get insights, suggestions and personalised summaries with interactive growth charts.

creator: theAsianparent - largest pregnancy & parenting app
descriptionHtml:
Discover a vibrant community for parents & pregnant women in this Asian parenting app.

A wealth of information about parenting, the bump, pregnancy, baby calendar, future baby, contraction timer, & baby development is now at your fingertips in theAsianparent app. With a single touch, find credible advice from our experienced community, & rich articles from experts. Pregnancy due & baby tracker in this Asian parenting app intelligently follows your child's amazing journey & provides support every step of the way.

Empower a happy & healthy pregnancy with the Asian Parents app pregnancy tracker. From tracking the bump, contraction timer, to track baby health, theAsianparent is an all-in-one baby app, supportive parenting community for pregnant moms and parents.

In this Asian parenting app: get nutrition advice, track baby growth, use contraction timer, & in-depth guides that cover your every concern. Articles in this Asian parents app deliver expert advice on your most urgent questions from pregnant moms and related to child development.

As an Asian parenting app, theAsianparent believes that everyone deserves a positive journey from pregnant phase to birth to every year of parenting. With this pregnancy and baby app, Moms & dads should have access to the information of millions of parents who share the experience of parenthood.

theAsianparent features:

👶 THE BABY CARE TRACKERS (New Features!)

You must be having questions about baby feeding schedule, baby poo, pee, etc. Fret not; we are here to help you with everything.

There’s no shortage of benefits of using our baby care trackers. It’s one of the best ways to easily and regularly check on your baby’s health. Baby Care Trackers help you regulate baby feeding schedule, baby nap time routine & baby poo & pee habits. We have 3 types of trackers which are:

Sleep Tracker: Use our baby sleep tracker that helps you track and learn about your baby’s sleep habits, and provides tips on improving them.
Diaper tracker: Identify baby’s poop & pee patterns, but it can also help you plan the diaper expenses accordingly.
Baby Feeding Tracker: It helps you track your baby’s feeding schedule in one place, monitor the time you spend nursing, how often your baby is feeding, which breast he/she last fed on, and much more.

So, start logging your baby's growth today on our new trackers to get insights, suggestions and personalised summaries with interactive growth charts.

👶PREGNANCY TRACKER & BABY TRACKER 🤰
- Ensure a healthy & happy pregnant mom journey with the pregnancy tracker app week by week.
- Get ultimate guide to the pregnant phase, the baby bump, pregnancy countdown, contraction from our baby tracker app etc.
- Keep tabs on the baby's development from the pregnant phase until your child is 6 years old on our baby tracking app.

👪INTERACT WITH OUR PARENTING COMMUNITY 💏
- Our parenting community is a perfect place to ask questions, participate in exciting contests & giveaways, share pregnancy / baby stories, photos, and tips with other parents just like you.
- Get advice on the bump, future baby, baby development, breastfeeding, & more.

📖 BABY & PARENTING FAMILY ARTICLES 📱
To help you sail through pregnancy & parenting journey, get access to the most reliable information with an arry of articles available on theAsianparent app.

🥘FOOD & NUTRITION🥛
- This feature allows you to learn about what food is safe to eat during pregnancy, confinement & when you're breastfeeding.

🎉 GREAT GIFTS! 🙌
- Participate in contests & giveaways, & you could win awesome gifts, vouchers, staycations, & more.

📷 BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE 📲
- Enjoy baby bump pregnancy stickers that you can click & share.
- Share the baby bump picture in a safe & private parent network.

Download theAsianparent app today & be a part of the largest community of Asian parents in the world.

With features like, ‘track my pregnancy’, ‘track my baby’- you’ll stay up-to-date with everything in your pregnancy & parenting journey. Articles in this app deliver expert advice on your most urgent questions from pregnant moms related to child development. 📝

As an Asian parenting app, theAsianparent believes that everyone deserves a positive journey from the pregnancy phase to birth to every year of parenting. With this pregnancy and baby app, mums & dads should have access to the information of millions of parents who share the experience of parenthood. 😀✅

PREGNANCY TRACKER
- With features like a pregnancy calendar, heartbeat monitor for pregnancy, and pregnancy baby countdown, our app will help you navigate every step of your pregnancy journey. We also offer a contraction timer to help you track your contractions and prepare for labour.

THE BABY CARE TRACKERS

Once your little one arrives, our track my baby feature allows you to monitor his/her growth and development.
There’s no shortage of benefits to using our baby care trackers. It’s one of the best ways to easily and regularly check on your baby’s health. Baby Care Trackers help you regulate baby feeding schedules, & baby poo & pee habits. We have 3 types of trackers which are:

- Sleep Tracker: Use our baby sleep tracker that helps you track and learn about your baby’s sleep habits, and provides tips on improving them.
- Diaper tracker: Identify baby’s poo & pee patterns, but it can also help you plan the diaper expenses accordingly.
- Baby Feeding Tracker: It helps you track your baby feeding schedule in one place, monitor the time you spend nursing, how often your baby is feeding, which breast he/she was last fed on, and much more.

So, start logging your baby's growth today on our new trackers to get insights, suggestions, and personalised summaries with interactive growth charts.

INTERACT WITH OUR PARENTING COMMUNITY
- Our parenting community is a perfect place to ask questions, participate in exciting contests & giveaways, and share pregnancy/baby stories, photos, and tips with other parents just like you.

- This feature allows you to learn what food is safe to eat during pregnancy, confinement & when you're breastfeeding.

So, start logging your baby's growth today on our new trackers to get insights, suggestions, and personalised summaries with interactive growth charts.

INTERACT WITH OUR PARENTING COMMUNITY
- Our parenting community is a perfect place to ask questions, participate in exciting contests & giveaways, and share pregnancy/baby stories, photos, and tips with other parents just like you.

BABY & PARENTING FAMILY ARTICLES
- With a simple tap of a button, you can read rich articles from experts. Our articles cover everything from pregnancy to parenting, baby development to breastfeeding, so you can be sure you're getting reliable information from experts.

FOOD & NUTRITION
- This feature allows you to learn what food is safe to eat during pregnancy, confinement & when you're breastfeeding.

BABY PHOTOS, MUSIC & MORE

- Enjoy baby bump pregnancy stickers that you can click & share.
- Share the baby bump picture in a safe & private parent network.

Overall, theAsianparent app is the perfect solution for expecting parents and new parents who want to stay informed, connected, and supported throughout every step of their pregnancy and parenting journey. So why wait? Download theAsianparent app today to access expert advice and guidance & be a part of the largest community of Asian parents in the world.
